Hey,

Both monitors are detected, you'll see both in gddccontrol.

ddccontrol -p always picks the first one, you can choose between both by
running:
ddccontrol pci:01:00.0-1
or
ddccontrol pci:01:00.0-2

(see ddccontrol -h for more details....)

Best regards,

Nicolas


